main event: A Project Blue Book file dated July 10, 1947, includes a report from Harmon AFB in Newfoundland with references to unidentified aerial phenomena.
interesting points: The file mentions a total of 4 associated photographs., The first image is a blurry black and white photo of a cloudy sky., One photo appears to show a bright, elongated object in the sky., There are no clear identifiable elements in the photographs., The report contains various diagrams and maps related to air operations.
